{"tid":1358604,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［拋磚］有無手足做銀行睇住大灣區project如火如荼想做d野","createTime":"2019-07-24T03:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T06:46:30.000Z","uid":270286,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a8dbc48e82ce8a6a2e3b5cbea8d0bc554cf2f283","tid":1358604,"uid":270286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:17:26.000Z","msg":"有朋友做獅子銀行<br />\n話有國企銀彈力推之下<br />\n全間bank上下都加速推緊好多大灣區project<br />\n依兩年會鋪天蓋地宣傳叫人上去消費，<br />\n加快將香港同中國融合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行內員工都唔敢出聲反對<br />\n老細一句唔好將政治立場帶入銀行<br />\n全部人無聲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港保衛戰唔止上街同光復街頭<br />\n各行各業好多魔鬼細節逐少逐少出賣香港<br />\n獅子銀行都叫飲香港奶水大<br />\n一隻眼開一隻眼閉出賣香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家有無咩建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf4619ef750792e691312263f8e9c43009d9963","tid":1358604,"uid":270286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:21:17.000Z","msg":"唔好比顧住搵錢既銀行做賣港幫兇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e479db7a6397643d5ddd64100ea754a073e5ace3","tid":1358604,"uid":216877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:04:17.000Z","msg":"唔至大貓，間間都係<br />\n明明大風險都要力推<br />\n做到心理唔平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67902af514c91e6ded2ee5fc692fbecf444300fd","tid":1358604,"uid":270286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T09:33:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40a3e2e6423ccefb5e9f5616c0e885de2306cf1e","tid":1358604,"uid":270286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep